---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-inner">
		<div class="footer-main">
			<div class="footer-brand">
				<span class="footer-icon" aria-hidden="true">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="36" height="36" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" fill="#f5c75c"/>
						<ellipse cx="32" cy="36" rx="20" ry="14" fill="#fff"/>
						<circle cx="26" cy="34" r="2.2" fill="#1f2a24"/>
						<circle cx="38" cy="34" r="2.2" fill="#1f2a24"/>
						<rect x="29" y="40" width="6" height="2" rx="1" fill="#2d6e4f"/>
					</svg>
				</span>
				<div>
					<p class="footer-title">家計ニュース</p>
					<p class="footer-tagline">子育て家庭のお金情報まとめ</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="footer-desc">
				毎朝8:00、AIが家計に直結する経済ニュースをまとめてお届け。
				掲載情報は要約のため、最終判断は公式情報をご確認ください。
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-copyright">
			<p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} 家計ニュース All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1f5239 0%, #163d2a 100%);
		color: #d8e7dc;
		padding: 2.5em 1em 2em;
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}
	.footer-inner {
		width: 1080px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.footer-main {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: center;
		padding-bottom: 1.5em;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(216, 231, 220, 0.15);
	}
	.footer-brand {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.7em;
	}
	.footer-icon {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 44px;
		height: 44px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
		border-radius: 50%;
	}
	.footer-title {
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #faf7ee;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}
	.footer-tagline {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		color: #f5c75c;
	}
	.footer-desc {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #d8e7dc;
	}
	.footer-copyright {
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 1.5em;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: rgba(216, 231, 220, 0.7);
	}
	.footer-copyright p {
		margin: 0;
	}
	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.footer-main {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.footer-brand {
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}
</style>
